==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: contraclockwise
<hw>contraclockwise</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>in the direction opposite
to the rotation of the hands of a clock; counterclockwise. Opposite of
<ant>clockwise</ant>.</def> <see>[Also See:
<er>sinistral</er>.]</see>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> counterclockwise, anticlockwise.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

